com.solacesystems.jcsmp

Interface SubscriptionStateProvider

  • Deprecated. 
    SubscriptionStateProvider is no longer supported and its use has no effect.

    @Deprecated
public interface SubscriptionStateProvider
    SubscriptionStateProvider is a callback interface for the application to provide a subscriber's current subscription state. Refer to JCSMPSession.getMessageConsumer(SubscriptionStateProvider, XMLMessageListener) and SubscriptionState for more details.

    • Method Summary

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods Deprecated Methods

      SubscriptionState getSubscriptionState()
      Deprecated. 
      This method returns the most recent subscription state of a subscriber.
